{
  "page": "Rimegate",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_North.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The north and the location of Rimegate\"><img alt=\"The north and the location of Rimegate\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/400px-The_North.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"431\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/600px-The_North.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/800px-The_North.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 12.2%; left: 70.6%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 9px; font-size: 9px;\"><img alt=\"The north and the location of Rimegate\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/9px-Wolff2.PNG\" title=\"Rimegate\" width=\"9\" height=\"9\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/14px-Wolff2.PNG 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/18px-Wolff2.PNG 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Rimegate</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a> and the location of Rimegate\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Rimegate</b>  is a castle along the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a> abandoned by the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's  Watch</a>. It is located between <a href=\"/index.php/Sable_Hall\" title=\"Sable Hall\">Sable Hall</a> to the west and the <a href=\"/index.php/Long_Barrow\" title=\"Long Barrow\">Long Barrow</a> to the east.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rimegate&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Night&#39;s Watch\">Lord Commander of the Night's Watch</a> tasked Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Olyver_Bracken\" title=\"Olyver Bracken\">Olyver Bracken</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Raymund_Mallery\" title=\"Raymund Mallery\">Raymund Mallery</a> with restoring the crumbling Rimegate and <a href=\"/index.php/Sable_Hall\" title=\"Sable Hall\">Sable Hall</a>, respectively, but the two former <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> rebelled from the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/50_AC\" title=\"50 AC\">50&#160;AC</a> with the intention to make the castles their seats as <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a>. Aided by <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, loyal brothers of the Night's Watch recaptured Rimegate and hanged Olyver's rebels. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walton_Stark_(son_of_Brandon)\" title=\"Walton Stark (son of Brandon)\">Walton Stark</a> beheaded Olyver with <a href=\"/index.php/Ice\" title=\"Ice\">Ice</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rimegate&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rimegate&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord Commander <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> intends to garrison the abandoned castles of Rimegate and <a href=\"/index.php/Hoarfrost_Hill\" title=\"Hoarfrost Hill\">Hoarfrost Hill</a>, and consults with <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Steward\" title=\"Lord Steward\">Lord Steward</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Bowen_Marsh\" title=\"Bowen Marsh\">Bowen Marsh</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/First_Builder\" title=\"First Builder\">First Builder</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Othell_Yarwyck\" title=\"Othell Yarwyck\">Othell Yarwyck</a> for their opinion of which <a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">wildling</a> chieftains would be best suited to hold the castles. Both men strongly reject his suggestions, with Marsh urging they be hanged for their deeds and Yarwyck claiming it was a lethal choice between \"bad\" and \"worse.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rimegate&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Jon Snow</b>: We have <a href=\"/index.php/Brogg\" title=\"Brogg\">Brogg</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Gavin_the_Trader\" title=\"Gavin the Trader\">Gavin the Trader</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Walrus\" title=\"Great Walrus\">Great Walrus</a>&#160;&#8230;&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/Howd_Wanderer\" title=\"Howd Wanderer\">Howd Wanderer</a> walks alone, <a href=\"/index.php/Tormund\" title=\"Tormund\">Tormund</a> says, but there’s still <a href=\"/index.php/Harle_the_Huntsman\" title=\"Harle the Huntsman\">Harle the Huntsman</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Harle_the_Handsome\" title=\"Harle the Handsome\">Harle the Handsome</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Blind_Doss\" title=\"Blind Doss\">Blind Doss</a>&#160;&#8230; <a href=\"/index.php/Ygon_Oldfather\" title=\"Ygon Oldfather\">Ygon Oldfather</a> commands a following, but most are his own sons and grandsons. He has eighteen wives, half of them stolen on raids. Which of these&#160;&#8230;<br />\n<b>Bowen Marsh</b>: None. I know all these men by their deeds. We should be fitting them for nooses, not giving them our castles.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Bowen_Marsh\" title=\"Bowen Marsh\">Bowen Marsh</a> on the potential garrison at Rimegate</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rimegate&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Map_of_Beyond_the_Wall\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Map of Beyond the Wall\">Map of Beyond the Wall</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, A Surfeit of Rulers.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_69\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 69\">Chapter 69</a>, Jon XIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Region_North\" title=\"Template:Region North\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Region_North&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Region North (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Region_North&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nThe <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">North</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Settlements</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;paddi